title: Black Widow v4 01-06 (2004|Marvel Knights)
description:
Titled "Right to Life", this 2004 limited series was written by Richard K. Morgan with art by Bill Sienkiewicz and published under the Marvel Knights banner and focuses on Natasha's attempts to escape her life of intrigue - without much success. Promotional info from the collected edition - "The deadliest agent in the Marvel Universe has finally gotten out of the spy game, and she's not asking for much, just a life of her own. When a sudden assassination attempt provides a harsh reality check, the former Soviet agent tracks a string of international killings that will lead her back to a Russia she can barely recognize."

These are archival scans of decent quality, without a scanner credit listed. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
